OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain mostly cloudy with some showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain, heavy at times,
OL,8,Falong with some drier periods. A very
OL,9,Fmild, rather humid night with a
OL,10,Ffreshening southerly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAnother cloudy day with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, some of which will
OL,14,Fbe heavy. Some drier periods too and
OL,15,Fperhaps brightening up over Argyll
OL,16,Fwith some late sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
